en.defaultValue: Saving-i account offers a distinct way to grow your money without traditional interest. It is a profit-sharing account where your funds are ethically invested in Sharia-approved activities. Instead of interest, you earn an Expected Profit Rate from the returns generated by these investments. The account features flexible access and is supervised by an independent Sharia committee. It's a simple, principled way to save.

• Nationality: Singapore citizen / Singapore permanent resident / foreigner residing in Singapore
  • Age requirement: Parents need to be 26 years old and above, Child needs to be below 18 years old
  • Service Charge S$0
  • No account fee for customers on eStatement
  • $2 per month for customers with paper statement

• Earn up to 4.0% p.a. with the Citi Interest Booster Account
  • Boost your returns with up to 2% cash back* (capped at S$2,000) on your Citi Cash Back+ Mastercard Credit Card when you spend min. S$500 for a period of 12 months. In addition, enjoy up to S$699 worth of exciting gifts. T&Cs apply.
  • Level up your financial literacy with wealth insights and bite-sized personal finance education content
  • Access to stocks, investment funds, FX and a wide range of other financial solutions, so you can invest easily, anytime and anywhere, with the Citi Mobile App
  • Achieve your goals and protect yourself from life's uncertainties with insurance solutions built around you and your changing needs
